{"tid":36713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將報復美國？路透：傳北京已列好企業名單","createTime":"2016-12-13T01:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T12:59:45.000Z","uid":35790,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0393868407fba8ae2ad03de678dd418316f2675d","tid":36713,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:32:55.000Z","msg":"將報復美國？路透：傳北京已列好企業名單 <br />\n2016-12-13 08:58 <br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<br />\n<br />\n美國準總統川普近來頻對中國開砲，昨天接受媒體訪問時直言， 美國未必受一中政策束縛，引發北京嗆聲「嚴重關切」。外媒報導，據傳川普頻頻放話， 惹怒中國，有不具名消息來源指出，北京可能會展開回擊，中共正列出一份商業利益清單 ，作為報復名單。 <br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導有不具名人士指出，如果川普態度持續強硬，北京可能會打擊報復在中國做 生意的美國公司。且根據在北京的可靠消息，共產黨正擬訂商業利益名單作為報復對象， 只要看美國有哪些商品是出口至中國的最大宗，很快就能瞭若指掌。 <br />\n<br />\n報導提到，有貿易政策專家指出，美國有30多州出口至中國的貿易金額超過10億美元，而 美國企業在中國的商業利益高達5千億美元，如果中國報復的話，這些都將處於危險之中 。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1915527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1915527&d=A2FilI2z%2B5TCIr3KZpWVfGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=62a0c37a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1915527&h=e452ea6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1915527</a>"},{"pid":"ccd129b05e372bce2ecd9e0c3d39f6bd935ee940","tid":36713,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:33:49.000Z","msg":"快，唔做正仆街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後香港變走私港"},{"pid":"4514ad6f2d0363f78eb8afe468fedbb57acfeb08","tid":36713,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:34:10.000Z","msg":"🍎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08bd27f0d749b27494436524eec7397659408dea","tid":36713,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:35:04.000Z","msg":"巧驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5174d556d6e7181bf36